## Appendix

### A. Project Structure
The project is based on Next.js 15 with the following key directories:
- `/app` - Next.js App Router pages
- `/components` - React components
- `/data` - Site metadata and content data
- `/layouts` - Page layout templates
- `/public` - Static assets

### B. Key Files to Modify
- `data/siteMetadata.js` - Site configuration
- `data/projectsData.js` - Portfolio projects data
- `app/page.tsx` - Home page
- `app/about/page.tsx` - About page
- `app/projects/page.tsx` - Projects page
- `components/Header.tsx` - Navigation header
- `components/Footer.tsx` - Footer component

### C. Resources
- Next.js Documentation: https://nextjs.org/docs
- Tailwind CSS Documentation: https://tailwindcss.com/docs
- Contentlayer Documentation: https://www.contentlayer.dev/docs

